const usefulLocations = [
  { name: 'Library', url: 'https://goo.gl/maps/2QwQwQwQwQwQwQwQ8' },
  { name: 'Student Union (SUB)', url: 'https://goo.gl/maps/8QwQwQwQwQwQwQwQ9' },
  { name: 'Financial Aid Office', url: 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Texas+Tech+Visitors+Center/@33.586274,-101.8727059,451m/data=!3m1!1e3!4m6!3m5!1s0x86fe12b3fdda2229:0xf2dd62b3c3e4e35a!8m2!3d33.5851357!4d-101.8724928!16s%2Fg%2F11clybv9yw?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI1MDkwMy4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D' },
  { name: 'Chick-fil-A', url: 'https://goo.gl/maps/4QwQwQwQwQwQwQwQ7' },
  { name: 'Starbucks', url: 'https://goo.gl/maps/6QwQwQwQwQwQwQwQ5' },
  { name: 'TTU Rec Center', url: 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Robert+H.+Ewalt+Student+Recreation+Center/@33.587013,-101.876964,17z' },
];

const Home: React.FC = () => {
  const [tab, setTab] = React.useState(0);

  return (
    <Box sx={{ background: ttuRed, minHeight: '100vh', fontFamily: 'Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif' }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ pt: 4 }}>
        <Box sx={{ mb: 4, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          <Typography variant="h2" sx={{ color: 'white', fontWeight: 'bold', mb: 2 }}>
            Texas Tech Student Info Portal
          </Typography>
          <Tabs value={tab} onChange={(_, v) => setTab(v)} centered textColor="inherit" indicatorColor="secondary">
            <Tab label="Students" />
            <Tab label="Useful Locations" />
            <Tab label="TTU Images" />
          </Tabs>
        </Box>
        {tab === 0 && (
          <Grid container spacing={3} justifyContent="center">
            {students.map((student, idx) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={idx}>
                <Card sx={{ background: 'white', borderRadius: 3, boxShadow: 3 }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: ttuRed, fontWeight: 'bold' }}>{student.name}</Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body1">R Number: {student.rNumber}</Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" color="error" sx={{ mt: 2 }} onClick={() => window.location.href = `/student-details?student=${idx}`}>View Details</Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        )}
        {tab === 1 && (
          <Grid container spacing={3} justifyContent="center">
            {usefulLocations.map((loc, idx) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={idx}>
                <Card sx={{ background: 'white', borderRadius: 3, boxShadow: 3 }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: ttuRed, fontWeight: 'bold' }}>{loc.name}</Typography>
                    <Button variant="outlined" color="error" sx={{ mt: 2 }} href={loc.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in Google Maps</Button>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        )}
        {tab === 2 && (
          <Grid container spacing={3} justifyContent="center">
            {ttuImages.map((img, idx) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={idx}>
                <Card sx={{ background: 'white', borderRadius: 3, boxShadow: 3 }}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <Box sx={{ height: 200, background: `url(${img}) center/cover`, borderRadius: 2 }} />
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        )}
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
